{"tid":2160292,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"其實遲下成個勞工市場俾大陸狗取代，香港人仲有咩工返？","createTime":"2020-08-16T23:58:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T10:28:07.000Z","uid":325200,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"167f051c71a31abd3383ef95a5f311d2fdd130af","tid":2160292,"uid":325200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T23:58:45.000Z","msg":"移民走既都移曬<br />\n留底既香港人可以做咩工？<br />\n工程？大陸狗150蚊一工，工程師人工得香港一半<br />\n醫護？大陸護士得萬幾蚊人工<br />\n會計？大陸會計萬幾蚊肯同你捱生捱死<br />\nIT ？ 好少少，聽講IT係大陸人工唔錯同吃香，但呀豬呀狗都讀，年年幾百萬畢業生第一志願做IT，入到騰訊，字母跳動做你就上左岸咁制<br />\n但競爭好大，你預左落到香港，一萬蚊一堆人同你做<br />\n<br />\n仲有咩行業穩陣取代唔到香港人？我唯一諗到真係一係做執屎師，一係做通渠佬，厭惡性行業"},{"pid":"388e1f1b8c7e2c2674c53d3de2ad4e650913527b","tid":2160292,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T01:07:10.000Z","msg":"咪被殖民<br />\n港豬做器官提供師囉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全民dna送中後"},{"pid":"cbaa93792901d1e7d89c7c5f87c98232d1b95667","tid":2160292,"uid":362827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T03:26:40.000Z","msg":"公務員"},{"pid":"e06e11313719c69ed29d3cc9c212780149bd0b4a","tid":2160292,"uid":325200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"388e1f1b8c7e2c2674c53d3de2ad4e650913527b","tid":2160292,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T01:07:10.000Z","msg":"咪被殖民<br />\n港豬做器官提供師囉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全民dna送中後"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-